('Can You Beat This EXO Quiz Score?', 'I scored 9/10 on the EXO fan trivia at kpopquiz.org! True EXO-Ls should be able to beat this. Play the quiz and show what you know! #EXO #EXOL #kpopquiz #kpopchallenge', 'K-pop Quiz Scores', 'score_challenge', 'https://kpopquiz.org', 'EXO', 'exo', 'Can You Beat My EXO Quiz Score?', 'True EXO-L fans should score higher than 9', '9/10', '90', false, 'draft', ARRAY['#kpop', '#EXO', '#EXOL', '#kpopquiz', '#kpopchallenge'], 'score_challenge', 165),
('Can You Beat This aespa Quiz Score?', 'I scored 8/10 on the aespa trivia quiz at kpopquiz.org! MY fans, are you ready to score higher? Test your aespa knowledge now! #aespa #MY #kpopquiz', 'K-pop Quiz Scores', 'score_challenge', 'https://kpopquiz.org', 'aespa', 'aespa', 'Can You Beat My aespa Score?', 'MY fans - are you ready to beat this?', '8/10', '80', false, 'draft', ARRAY['#kpop', '#aespa', '#MY', '#kpopquiz', '#kpopchallenge'], 'score_challenge', 166),
('Can You Beat This NewJeans Quiz Score?', 'I got a perfect 10/10 on the NewJeans quiz at kpopquiz.org! Bunnies - can you match a perfect score? Play now and find out! #NewJeans #Bunnies #kpopquiz #kpopchallenge', 'K-pop Quiz Scores', 'score_challenge', 'https://kpopquiz.org', 'NewJeans', 'newjeans', 'I scored PERFECT on the NewJeans Quiz!', 'Bunnies - can you match a 10/10?', '10/10', '100', false, 'draft', ARRAY['#kpop', '#NewJeans', '#Bunnies', '#kpopquiz', '#kpopchallenge'], 'score_challenge', 167),
('Can You Beat This SEVENTEEN Quiz Score?', 'I scored 9/10 on the SEVENTEEN fan quiz at kpopquiz.org! CARATs - do you know your 13 members well enough to beat me? Play the quiz now! #SEVENTEEN #CARAT #kpopquiz', 'K-pop Quiz Scores', 'score_challenge', 'https://kpopquiz.org', 'SEVENTEEN', 'seventeen', 'Can You Beat My SEVENTEEN Score?', 'CARATs - do you know all 13 members'' facts?', '9/10', '90', false, 'draft', ARRAY['#kpop', '#SEVENTEEN', '#CARAT', '#SVT', '#kpopquiz'], 'score_challenge', 168),
('Can You Beat This (G)I-DLE Quiz Score?', 'I scored 8/10 on the (G)I-DLE trivia at kpopquiz.org! Neverlands - think you know Soyeon, Miyeon, Minnie, Yuqi and Shuhua better than me? Play now! #GIDLE #kpopquiz', 'K-pop Quiz Scores', 'score_challenge', 'https://kpopquiz.org', '(G)I-DLE', 'g-i-dle', 'Can You Beat My (G)I-DLE Score?', 'Neverlands - show what you know', '8/10', '80', false, 'draft', ARRAY['#kpop', '#GIDLE', '#Neverland', '#kpopquiz', '#kpopchallenge'], 'score_challenge', 169),
('Can You Beat This IVE Quiz Score?', 'I scored 7/10 on the IVE quiz at kpopquiz.org. DIVE fans - can you score higher? Test your IVE knowledge and show off! #IVE #DIVE #kpopquiz #kpopchallenge', 'K-pop Quiz Scores', 'score_challenge', 'https://kpopquiz.org', 'IVE', 'ive', 'Can You Beat My IVE Quiz Score?', 'DIVE fans - do better than 7/10', '7/10', '70', false, 'draft', ARRAY['#kpop', '#IVE', '#DIVE', '#kpopquiz', '#kpopchallenge'], 'score_challenge', 170),
